{"tid":2140407,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"疫情期間 PS4 遊戲銷量幾乎翻了一番 其中大部分都是數位版本。","createTime":"2020-08-05T03:47:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T12:23:36.000Z","uid":56731,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"685bea0b4d112763b9ee6f6c42a7766545568010","tid":2140407,"uid":56731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:47:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-08/52be29f0-d630-11ea-b73f-7a4dbf984068\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-08%2F52be29f0-d630-11ea-b73f-7a4dbf984068&h=e02b7f03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就在不久前，Sony 公佈了本財年第四季度的財報。在各項數據中首先抓到我們眼球的是遊戲部門的業績，在這一季中 PS4 遊戲的銷量達到了 9,100 萬份，相比去年同時期的 4,980 萬份，漲幅足足有 83% 之多。在這之中，第一方獨佔作品的受歡迎程度相當之高，以《最後生還者 Part II》為首的多款遊戲在 Q4 中總共賣出了 1,850 萬份，隔年增幅達 58%。<br />\n<br />\n在疫情影響下，有這樣的結果其實在意料之中。而且因為人們減少出門的關係，在售出的遊戲中有 74% 都是數位版本。另外 PS Plus 服務的訂閱量，也從一年前的 4,150 萬上升到了 4,490 萬。至於 PS4 硬體的銷量則如預期一樣仍保持一個下降的趨勢，第四季售出 190 萬台的數字雖然比前一季（140 萬台）要多，但相比去年同時期（320 萬台）還是減少了 41%。在 PS5 到來之前，這個勢頭多半是不會有太大變化。<br />\n<br />\n「盡管居家辦公、無法出差等因素造成了不小的障礙，但我們還是採取了必要的措施，為了讓 PS5 如期在今年聖誕季推出，一切準備都在按計畫進行當中。」Sony 在財報中這麼寫道。此外遊戲部門整體在 Q4 貢獻了 6,060 億日圓的銷售額，比去年同時期的 4,570 億要高出了不少。但與此同時包括電視、手機、相機、電影等在內的幾乎所有部門，在這一季內業績均有所下滑。<br />\n<br />\n不過 Sony 集團整體的銷售額達到了約 1.97 兆日圓，對比去年同期（1.92 兆日圓）有一定的提升。營運收入則來到 2,280 億日圓，相比一年前的 2,300 億日圓有小幅度的下降。<br />\n<a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/sony-financial-earnings-ps4-game-sales-pandemic-090239488.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2Fsony-financial-earnings-ps4-game-sales-pandemic-090239488.html&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZeagEiaVT8aWta%2BTWQuzHxyy8%3D&h=7907c8b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/sony-financial-earnings-ps4-game-sales-pandemic-090239488.html</a>"},{"pid":"d6cfc470da842414160d1e2fa528f3819b535cc6","tid":2140407,"uid":56731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:49:31.000Z","msg":"tldr; 一季賣咗1,850萬隻game,74%數位版,6,060 億yen銷售額"},{"pid":"ee146b4b95fc8313cc865d14fc6f64b858bb5450","tid":2140407,"uid":74970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:53:33.000Z","msg":"last of us 2 <span class=\"maroon\">為首</span>既第一方驚<br />\n今季除左lou，對馬，仲有d咩？"},{"pid":"7464d1ca41b7391c609de42c99c87b70ad112507","tid":2140407,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee146b4b95fc8313cc865d14fc6f64b858bb5450","tid":2140407,"uid":74970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:53:33.000Z","msg":"last of us 2 <span class=\"maroon\">為首</span>既第一方驚<br />\n今季除左lou，對馬，仲有d咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:57:24.000Z","msg":"高達"},{"pid":"d30e1582c914e9c86645d8081988b50aa86ad7e6","tid":2140407,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee146b4b95fc8313cc865d14fc6f64b858bb5450","tid":2140407,"uid":74970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:53:33.000Z","msg":"last of us 2 <span class=\"maroon\">為首</span>既第一方驚<br />\n今季除左lou，對馬，仲有d咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:59:10.000Z","msg":"應該唔限今年"},{"pid":"5a3e80791ab8c1f8430c4627da10e931a843c699","tid":2140407,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T04:23:06.000Z","msg":"成日等特價買數位版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"526ef8dc249c395eac794566c11f8a097b5be6d7","tid":2140407,"uid":113944,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T04:26:07.000Z","msg":"時勢造英雄姐, 動森同一道理"},{"pid":"452b33d32a69915f4dd8887f03c2e2e0563b718f","tid":2140407,"uid":233851,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T04:27:03.000Z","msg":"除左fans買典藏版之外，大部份玩家都係買數位版啦，少量單機game會有人買實體爆完放既"},{"pid":"97af8f09df99c3778fbff4325e9a0644a76006bc","tid":2140407,"uid":270619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T06:12:57.000Z","msg":"animal crossing 個銷量先恐怖"},{"pid":"dfc1743a7b5262b2ffc7a263348449dc9